name: ZohoWiki
overview: Zoho Wiki is a hosted wiki service for free, which have all the basic functionality of wiki software like create, edit web pages, email and RSS notifications and much more features. You can use Zoho Wiki as Enterprise wiki, Group wiki, Personal wiki, Private wiki, Public wiki. Here, who creates the wiki is the administrator/owner of that wiki. Layout, look and feel customization based upon your company website theme using CSS. Custom domain, Custom Favicon will give more feel like your website. Try one month trial version today!!!
